<plot>People leaving in an isolated mountain village near the frontier are as rude as the land - and often resort to smuggling to make ends meet. Any disloyalty is to punished, not by the law, but tradition. Now, when Francisca, a wild gypsy girl, esteemed by all, pays attention to more than one man, trouble erupts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?625466</url></doc>
